    ],
    "text": "Commander of the Sri Lanka Navy Pays Courtesy Call on Inspector General of Police Following Promotion to Admiral",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      573.57,
      532.94,
      614.45
    ],
    "text": "Following his promotion to the rank of Admiral, the Commander of the Sri Lanka Navy, Admiral Kanchana Banagoda, paid a courtesy call on the Inspector General of Police, Attorney-at-Law Priyantha Weerasooriya, at Police Headquarters on 30 June 2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      628.89,
      535.47,
      669.77
    ],
    "text": "During the meeting, the Inspector General of Police congratulated Admiral Banagoda on his promotion from the rank of Vice Admiral to Admiral and conveyed his best wishes on behalf of the Sri Lanka Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      684.32,
      532.05,
      725.21
    ],
    "text": "The Inspector General of Police also expressed his appreciation for the close cooperation and valuable support extended by Admiral Banagoda to the Sri Lanka Police in the discharge of his duties as Commander of the Sri Lanka Navy.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      82.58,
      161.44,
      410.22,
      182.51
    ],
    "text": "D/Media/Out/1088/2026 2026.07.01 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dba 1550",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      31.91,
      539.75,
      72.79
    ],
    "text": "A group of senior police officers attended the occasion. As a token of appreciation and goodwill, the Inspector General of Police presented a commemorative memento to Admiral Kanchana Banagoda.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
